begin_memory_text: I had a very good chat with a 25 year old from Michigan....very matured, personable young gentleman with a strong head on his shoulders. middle_memory_text: My chat partner was easy going and great listener, respectful and overall a great young man. He needed to get into work force right after high school because of his dad's passing.  I shared my family background, my college student daughter and her activities and my values towards life, raising family and dealing with covid.
end_memory_text: We talked about how we are taking care of ourselves with covid situation, and how we are working from home for last 7 months, which we both agreed we enjoy.  Teleworking gives so much flexibility and also lets you balance life properly.  We also talked about the current generation and their desire to have finer things in life and how they like to live in the moment without worrying or saving for future.
